        "markdown_formatted": "## Meeting Purpose\n\n[Define the new technical QA process for DevRel documents.](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=34.0)\n\n## Key Takeaways\n\n  - [**New Process:** Make direct technical edits using Google Docs' \"Track Changes\" feature.](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=89.0)\n  - [**Rationale:** This eliminates a manual step for editors, streamlining the content pipeline.](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=120.0)\n  - [**Focus:** QA is strictly for technical accuracy (e.g., code, workflows), not editorial style or links.](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=137.0)\n  - [**Action:** Segun will re-edit prior work by EOD tomorrow and complete 5 new articles by early next week.](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=239.0)\n\n## Topics\n\n### Problem: Inefficient QA Workflow\n\n  - [The previous QA process was inefficient, requiring editors to manually implement suggested changes from comments.](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=120.0)\n  - [This created unnecessary work and slowed the content pipeline.](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=120.0)\n\n### Solution: Direct Technical Edits\n\n  - [The new process requires direct edits in Google Docs using \"Track Changes.\"](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=89.0)\n  - [**Procedure:**](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=89.0)\n    1.  [**Make the edit directly** in the document.](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=89.0)\n    2.  [**Add a comment** explaining the rationale for the change.](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=145.0)\n  - [**Scope:**](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=137.0)\n      - [**Focus:** Technical accuracy for a developer audience (e.g., code, workflows, specs).](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=137.0)\n      - [**Out of Scope:** Editorial style, internal links, or non-technical content (e.g., app registration steps).](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=163.0)\n\n## Next Steps\n\n  - [**Segun:**](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=239.0)\n      - [Re-edit all prior QA work using the new process (due EOD tomorrow).](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=239.0)\n      - [Submit the first re-edited article for review before continuing.](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=279.0)\n      - [Complete 5 new articles (due early next week).](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=259.0)\n  - [**Najam:**](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=259.0)\n      - [Assign 5 new articles to Segun (by EOD today or tomorrow).](https://fathom.video/share/z1ZxS6DtGvjp78Uz-N4uxaRFn7SVRkLr?tab=summary&timestamp=259.0)\n"
